title: The Abt Inspiration Studio
description:
If you're looking for ideas to help redesign your kitchen look no further than Abt's Inspiration Studio designed by Mick De Giulio.  Encompassing over 10,000 feet of floorspace, this one-of-a-kind showroom features 12 unique kitchen builds, each based on a suite of premium kitchen appliances from a respected brand. 

See more details here at Abt.com: http://www.abt.com/inspiration-studio
